  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t从昨天开始，北京多座大学就开始放假遣学生回家，广州也爆出来要求大学生“立刻返乡”，甚至有大学生露宿街头，生怕他们复刻六四。<br/>\r\n北京：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWQyZWU2NmE4MGRiMDllZmNlNDU5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5d2ee66a80db09efce459.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5d2ee66a80db09efce459.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5d2ee66a80db09efce459.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n这是一天前广州的大学，紧急让学生返乡，早早埋下伏笔……<b>要是放在十年前，谁能想到江泽民会被当成胡耀邦来防？</b><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjFhZjY5ZjVjMTFjOTMxMzUxNWQ3LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f1af69f5c11c9313515d7.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f1af69f5c11c9313515d7.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f1af69f5c11c9313515d7.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzlmYTZjN2VkOTUxZGU0NDdhZWM2LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/39fa6c7ed951de447aec6.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/39fa6c7ed951de447aec6.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/39fa6c7ed951de447aec6.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
